!body

%h1 Semicolons

%p Semicolons are only needed where necessary to resolve ambiguity. In order for this to work, binary operators should not appear at the beginning of a new line.

%pre <<EOF
    // This is fine.
    a := 1 + 2 +
        3

    // This is two statements: (b := 1 + 2) and (+3)
    b := 1 + 2
        + 3
EOF
